data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the prestigious King and Bear subdivision! Presenting a meticulously renovated 4-bedroom home that seamlessly blends modern elegance with timeless charm. Step into a world of sophistication with stained concrete flooring that exudes both durability and style. The heart of this residence boasts a gas fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for those chilly evenings. Every detail has been carefully considered, from the state-of-the-art security camera system ensuring peace of mind to the exquisite outdoor space. Embrace the outdoor oasis featuring a fully equipped outdoor kitchen and a captivating fire pit, perfect for entertaining or relaxing in the privacy of your own haven. Whether you' hosting a soiree or enjoying a quit evening under the stars, this home offers the ideal settings with its beautifully designed outdoor lighting and its prime location in the exclusive King and Bear community and an array of renovations that elevate the living experience, this property invites you to indulge in a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication.
